{"tid":2240288,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陸富豪攜巨款潛逃台灣 遭遞解出境","createTime":"2020-10-12T14:20:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T14:51:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"30232dfde3e800262e657f3ce479e8cabd46f1e2","tid":2240288,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:20:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201012/RBWEWOPBZJDKREIQZDT6WTROWA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201012%2FRBWEWOPBZJDKREIQZDT6WTROWA%2F&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V8yzqlNZT0%2FxJNtMGMfIkD0%3D&h=4f1ff87d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201012%2FRBWEWOPBZJDKREIQZDT6WTROWA%2F&h=ae294c09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201012/RBWEWOPBZJDKREIQZDT6WTROWA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n陸富豪攜巨款潛逃台灣 遭遞解出境<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/IgO7qPt19g4q--DimIyqMVVdOLc=/1575x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/A4HVQIJHUBEFNF6YUT6K2XIDCI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FIgO7qPt19g4q--DimIyqMVVdOLc%3D%2F1575x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FA4HVQIJHUBEFNF6YUT6K2XIDCI.jpg&h=43c8c837&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n張子毅<br />\n<br />\n大陸富豪、吉林文投集團負責人張子毅，去年涉嫌非法吸金逾1.1億港元，他為了逃避追緝，竟豪花500萬港元買通人蛇集團，帶着懷孕女友、黃金及字畫偷渡赴台。台媒最新報道，台警接報後突擊拉人，落難富豪承認非法入境及供出偷渡路線，不獲起訴，現時已被遞解出境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n供出偷渡路線免起訴<br />\n<br />\n現年44歲的張子毅在2012年創立「吉林文投集團」，集團號稱資產規模達17億港元，隨後設投資基金，以投資藝術品買賣、理財產品等名義，向大眾非法集資。去年3月，長春市公安局通報，張子毅涉嫌「非法吸收公眾存款罪」立案調查，未料對方已行蹤不明。<br />\n<br />\n原來張子毅風光時，多次赴台旅遊，由姓鍾台籍導遊帶着觀光，當他出事後也只想到台灣，今年3月帶同懷孕6個半月的女友，從福建寧德市搭船，偷渡到基隆港上岸後，在鍾男幫助下入住文華東方、W酒店。台警後來透過「海峽兩岸共同打擊犯罪及司法互助協議管道」，獲告知有偷渡客赴台，其於3月逮捕張子毅和其女友，查扣港幣、歐元現鈔，合計約5千萬元（約1,300萬港元），另外還有多幅清朝字畫及金條。<br />\n<br />\n張子毅落網後坦言喜歡台灣的環境，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"1ebfeb1dffff920e63b5955bb31df85e6add88b5","tid":2240288,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:24:20.000Z","msg":"台灣有冇出返張收據比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f23f34746a746791013d1d56cadf532c41478f","tid":2240288,"uid":52594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T14:51:44.000Z","msg":"可以先充公，再遞解"}]}